Package: automagic
Type: Package
Title: Automagically Install Required R Packages
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Cole Brokamp
Maintainer: Cole Brokamp <cole.brokamp@gmail.com>
Description: This package parses R code in a given directory for R
    packages and attempts to install them from CRAN or GitHub.
License: GPL
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.0)
Imports:
    knitr,
    formatR,
    pacman,
    githubinstall
URL: https://github.com/cole-brokamp/automagic
BugReports: https://github.com/cole-brokamp/automagic/issues
